{"tid":1222340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期日重遊唔遊行好","createTime":"2019-06-14T11:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T11:54:48.000Z","uid":36811,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c507dd9cf39928204d924dcf30a3cbf4f20dd400","tid":1222340,"uid":36811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"唔好屌住 唔係叫大家唔出  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係想問下大家有無諗過<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">直接去政總</span></strong></span><br />\n唔去再哂時間去維園比班黑警撚<br />\n<br />\n上星期日大家有出黎嘅話 都肯定比班黑警玩過<br />\n點你兜遠路 唔肯開路 企係度曬3粒鐘<br />\n玩到你無力抗爭<br />\n<br />\n重有<br />\n遊行數字count唔count到根本都唔係重點<br />\n黑警會9up作細數 民陣自己識做count翻我地咪得<br />\n<br />\n所以不如保留體力直接去圍政總算<br />\n有無得諗？"},{"pid":"0f2e17d9697a84a71f045a10a9467ddbe23a9530","tid":1222340,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"圍空城? 標題黨已經想屌你<br />\n你記唔記得9/6 做咩黎<br />\n二來個路線會變到好撚複雜"}]}